commits.message:
Merge pull request #198929 from r-ryantm/auto-update/yq-go

yq-go: 4.29.1 -> 4.29.2

crimson-pro: init at unstable-2022-08-30

A professionally produced redesign of Crimson by Jacques Le Bailly.
https://github.com/Fonthausen/CrimsonPro

gym: 0.21.0 -> 0.26.2

add importlib-metadata as dependency when python < 3.10

alice: init at 2.003

Open-source font by Ksenia Erulevich https://github.com/cyrealtype/Alice

cppcheck: fix broken hash

The original hash is for https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/4a17dcb and the new hash is for https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/ef1c70f.

linuxKernel.kernels.linux_5_19: drop

The 5.19.x series has reached EOL, and is no longer supported upstream.

percona-server56: drop

Percona Server for MySQL 5.6 is no more maintained due to the EOL of MySQL 5.6.
See https://www.percona.com/downloads/Percona-Server-5.6/LATEST/.

A bit hard to list all the potential security issues affecting it but CVE-2021-27928
should be one of them.

commits.message:
Merge pull request #198929 from r-ryantm/auto-update/yq-go

yq-go: 4.29.1 -> 4.29.2

crimson-pro: init at unstable-2022-08-30

A professionally produced redesign of Crimson by Jacques Le Bailly.
https://github.com/Fonthausen/CrimsonPro

gym: 0.21.0 -> 0.26.2

add importlib-metadata as dependency when python < 3.10

alice: init at 2.003

Open-source font by Ksenia Erulevich https://github.com/cyrealtype/Alice

cppcheck: fix broken hash

The original hash is for https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/4a17dcb and the new hash is for https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/ef1c70f.

linuxKernel.kernels.linux_5_19: drop

The 5.19.x series has reached EOL, and is no longer supported upstream.

percona-server56: drop

Percona Server for MySQL 5.6 is no more maintained due to the EOL of MySQL 5.6.
See https://www.percona.com/downloads/Percona-Server-5.6/LATEST/.

A bit hard to list all the potential security issues affecting it but CVE-2021-27928
should be one of them.

commits.message:
Merge pull request #198929 from r-ryantm/auto-update/yq-go

yq-go: 4.29.1 -> 4.29.2

crimson-pro: init at unstable-2022-08-30

A professionally produced redesign of Crimson by Jacques Le Bailly.
https://github.com/Fonthausen/CrimsonPro

gym: 0.21.0 -> 0.26.2

add importlib-metadata as dependency when python < 3.10

alice: init at 2.003

Open-source font by Ksenia Erulevich https://github.com/cyrealtype/Alice

cppcheck: fix broken hash

The original hash is for https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/4a17dcb and the new hash is for https://github.com/danmar/cppcheck/commit/ef1c70f.

linuxKernel.kernels.linux_5_19: drop

The 5.19.x series has reached EOL, and is no longer supported upstream.

percona-server56: drop

Percona Server for MySQL 5.6 is no more maintained due to the EOL of MySQL 5.6.
See https://www.percona.com/downloads/Percona-Server-5.6/LATEST/.

A bit hard to list all the potential security issues affecting it but CVE-2021-27928
should be one of them.
